---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="About" 
  description="About Bernard McWeeney — IT administrator, web developer, and technology enthusiast based in Dublin, Ireland."
>
  <div class="container py-8 md:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <header class="mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">
          About
        </h1>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="prose">
        <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
          Hi, I'm Bernard — an IT administrator based in Dublin, Ireland. I work in education technology, 
          managing Microsoft 365 environments and Google Workspace deployments across multiple institutions.
        </p>

        <h2>What I Do</h2>
        <p>
          By day, I handle the technical infrastructure for educational organizations — from bulk user management 
          and license provisioning to security auditing and compliance. I spend a lot of time in PowerShell, 
          automating the repetitive tasks that would otherwise eat up entire days.
        </p>
        <p>
          By night (and weekends), I build web projects. This site runs on Astro and is hosted on Cloudflare Workers. 
          I'm particularly interested in static site generators, modern CSS, and building tools that solve real problems.
        </p>

        <h2>Current Projects</h2>
        <p>
          I've been working on a few things lately:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Parish Core</strong> — A WordPress plugin for Catholic parish management, featuring liturgical calendar integration and mass scheduling</li>
          <li><strong>PowerShell automation scripts</strong> — For Google Drive file management, Windows ESU activation, and Microsoft 365 administration</li>
          <li><strong>This site</strong> — Always iterating on the design and adding new features</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
        <p>
          The tools I use most often:
        </p>
        <div class="not-prose flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-4">
          <span class="badge">PowerShell</span>
          <span class="badge">Microsoft 365</span>
          <span class="badge">Google Workspace</span>
          <span class="badge">Astro</span>
          <span class="badge">TypeScript</span>
          <span class="badge">Tailwind CSS</span>
          <span class="badge">Cloudflare</span>
          <span class="badge">WordPress</span>
          <span class="badge">PHP</span>
        </div>

        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          I'm always happy to chat about tech, answer questions, or explore collaboration opportunities. 
          You can reach me at:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@bernardmcweeney.com">hello@bernardmcweeney.com</a></li>
          <li>X (Twitter): <a href="https://x.com/BMcWeeneyIE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@BMcWeeneyIE</a></li>
          <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/BernardMcWeeney" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BernardMcWeeney</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Card -->
      <div class="card p-6 mt-10 bg-[var(--color-brand-muted)] border-[var(--color-brand)]/30">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">
          Want to work together?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mt-2">
          I'm open to freelance projects and consulting work, particularly around Microsoft 365 administration 
          and web development.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@bernardmcweeney.com" class="btn btn-primary mt-4">
          Get in touch →
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>